<%- include('../partials/topbar') %>
<%- include('../partials/ticker') %>
<%- include('../partials/slider') %>
<%- include('../partials/auth-buttons') %>

<section class="match-page with-home-bg">
  <main class="container match-layout">
    <article class="match-card-main">
      <div class="match-hero-card">
        <div class="match-league"><%= match.league %></div>
        <% if (match.hotMatch) { %><div class="hot-match-badge">🔥 HOT MATCH</div><% } %>
        <h1><%= match.match %></h1>
        <div class="match-time">🕒 <%= fmtDateTime(match.time || match.postDate) || fmtDate(match.postDate) %> WIB</div>
        <div class="teams-box">
          <div class="team-side"><span>HOME</span><strong><%= match.home %></strong></div>
          <div class="versus">VS</div>
          <div class="team-side"><span>AWAY</span><strong><%= match.away %></strong></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <section class="ai-panel">
        <div class="section-title">🤖 AI Prediction</div>
        <div class="percent-grid">
          <div class="percent-card"><span>HOME WIN</span><strong><%= match.percent.home %>%</strong><div class="bar"><i style="width:<%= match.percent.home %>%"></i></div></div>
          <div class="percent-card"><span>DRAW</span><strong><%= match.percent.draw %>%</strong><div class="bar"><i style="width:<%= match.percent.draw %>%"></i></div></div>
          <div class="percent-card"><span>AWAY WIN</span><strong><%= match.percent.away %>%</strong><div class="bar"><i style="width:<%= match.percent.away %>%"></i></div></div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="prediction-picks">
        <div class="pick-box"><span>1X2</span><strong><%= match.pick %></strong></div>
        <div class="pick-box"><span>OVER/UNDER</span><strong><%= match.ou %></strong></div>
        <div class="pick-box"><span>PREDIKSI SKOR</span><strong><%= match.score %></strong></div>
      </section>

      <section class="match-analysis">
        <h2>Analisa <%= match.match %></h2>
        <p>Halaman ini dibuat otomatis dari data prediksi parlay terbaru. Pertandingan <strong><%= match.match %></strong> masuk dalam kompetisi <strong><%= match.league %></strong> dan memiliki rekomendasi pilihan <strong><%= match.pick %></strong>, opsi <strong><%= match.ou %></strong>, serta estimasi skor <strong><%= match.score %></strong>.</p>
        <p>Persentase AI disusun sebagai indikator tambahan berdasarkan nama tim, status liga, dan pola prediksi otomatis. Gunakan data ini sebagai bahan bacaan tambahan sebelum menentukan pilihan.</p>
      </section>

      <% if (relatedMatches.length) { %>
        <section class="related-matches">
          <div class="section-title">🔥 Match Terkait</div>
          <div class="match-mini-grid">
            <% relatedMatches.forEach(function(item){ %>
              <a href="<%= matchUrl(item) %>" class="mini-match-card">
                <% if (item.hotMatch) { %><span>HOT</span><% } %>
                <strong><%= item.match %></strong>
                <small><%= item.league %></small>
              </a>
            <% }) %>
          </div>
        </section>
      <% } %>

      <div class="back-actions">
        <a href="/prediksi-parlay" class="read-btn">← Kembali ke Prediksi Parlay</a>
        <% if (match.postSlug) { %><a href="/prediksi-parlay/<%= match.postSlug %>" class="read-btn secondary">Lihat Artikel Induk</a><% } %>
      </div>
    </article>

    <%- include('../partials/sidebar-blog', { latestPosts, ads }) %>
  </main>
</section>

<%- include('../partials/footer') %>
<%- include('../partials/quick-menu') %>
